'''Bowvines''' were speckled plants growing on [[Belsavis/Legends|Belsavis]] that grew fruit. The fragile fruit bruised easily, and required careful packing and handling.<ref name="Taster's Choice">{{StoryCite|story=Taster's Choice: The Tale of Jabba's Chef|book=Tales from Jabba's Palace}}</ref>

